<div id="lab11"></div>

<h3 id="task-scheduler">Task Scheduler</h3>

<p><i>Highlight: </i> Legen‚Ä¶ wait for it <br /></p>

<p>Concurrent syncSM that scrolls through text to display the string ‚ÄúLegen ‚Ä¶ wait for it ‚Ä¶ DARY!!‚Äù, which is too big to fit on the LCD screen.</p>

